quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  36,71,"Koo, shibalolangakhwo mbu khwabaloonjela okhurulana khumilimo chia emikhono chiefu tsisolo tsiemiruko, etsia barukanga."
  36,72,"Ne nikhubanguyisilia etsindi mutsisolo etso tsiabaninangakhwo, ne etsindi batsiliitsaanga."
  36,73,"Ne bo banyoolanga mutsisolo etso akobukhonyi nende ebinywebwa, kho mana shibakhupanga orio tawe?"
  36,74,"Ne batila abanyasaye bandi habundu wa Nyasaye mbu khobanyoole obukhoonyi."
  36,75,"Shibalinyala okhubakhonya tawe halali abo nibo baliba abasikari babu olwa balikhwitsila."
  36,76,"Mana amakhuwa kabu kalakhubelesia tawe. Toto efwe khwamanya kabafisanga nende kabaretsaanga habulafu."
  36,77,"Ne omundu shalolanga ta mbu khwamuloonga okhurulana nende indonyande ya amatsi kolwibulo, ne lola awosa, naaba omuseeri wa habulafu."
  36,78,"Ne nakhuchelasilia, naye yebilila okhulongwa khukhwe. Mana naboola mbu: “Ni wina oyo ulilamusia ebikumba nibimalile okhubulungukha?”"
  36,79,"Boola mbu: “Alibilamusia ulia wabiloonga olwokhuranjilila, naye ni Omumanyi muno wabuli okhuloonga khwoosi."
  36,80,"Ulia wabakholela okhunyoola omulilo okhurula khumusala omubisi, mana nimunyoola okhubwana omulilo okhurulana ninakwo.""
  36,81,"Koo, waloonga likulu nende eshialo shanyala okhulonga bafwana ninabo tawe? Khulwa shina, naye niye Omuloonji Omukhongo, Omumanyi muno?"
  36,82,"Toto likhuwa lilie niyenya eshindu, ashiboolela butswa mbu: “Ba!” Ni shiba."
  36,83,"Mana yatswenukha ulia wobwami bwa buli eshindu buli mumukhono kukwe, ne ewuwe niwo wamulikalusibwa."